
this C++ code dont even compile but might be used to make a guis under
QT3 provided one find out how to plug in a good scripting interpreter
inside. I made a tentative with some XML syntax for input. I also
tried to embed QSA (trolltech Javascript interpreter for QT) but it
requires too much work to bind most of QT3 to it. I had big problems
with Python and posix threads used by many QT3 implementations.

Please fill free to reuse and enhance this code (under a GNU license
please) which don't compile and don't work.

